    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic and reliable ride! This vehicle is in good condition, showing it has been well-cared for and is ready for its next adventure. With a clean interior and a smooth driving experience, it offers great value for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels wonderful.",
